{"tid":2286970,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"曾經有一場真摯嘅性愛擺在我的面前 ,但我冇去珍惜","createTime":"2020-11-15T12:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T07:28:39.000Z","uid":375055,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2d9960acae67d1a56c2a6884ed3c81848dbdaa","tid":2286970,"uid":375055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mHBrGR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mHBrGR.jpg&h=fee61bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等到了失去的時候才後悔莫及<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,相信連登巴絲都有過咁嘅經歷。<br />\n  <br />\n有睇過我之前個post就知道我入左ust之後我前女友為咗個airpod pro比mk仔中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,而我由約佢出嚟到比佢狠狠拒絕嗰刻對條臭雞已經釋懷。決定唔要辜負ust science仔呢個身份,去溝bba女神。<br />\n   <br />\n我收番ust啲毒女令我jer都扯唔起呢句說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,喺我摺拉巴嗰陣,遇到一個超靚嘅bba師姐,可能我有啲靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,佢竟然主動過尼同我講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。點知佢第一句問我,你係咪讀science架我想問你借啲notes比我細佬溫書啊。而家諗起佢嗰刻嘅笑容真係好撚甜,諗起佢收咗我份notes開心嘅樣都夠我打飛機6日。<br />\n   <br />\n  我知d連仔睇到呢到實話我ff too much<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> but this is all true. 個師姐後來仲叫我join佢個soc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一齊玩,當係多謝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我無法抗拒嗰對楚楚可憐嘅大眼睛,我應承佢嘅速度(2.99秒)仲快過我平時打飛機0.01秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,於是我就join左佢嘅soc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n   係soc房入面,無論組爸組媽點撚9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,我嘅眼光只停留係師姐到。玩完之後,班撚樣留低我同女神執房,突然間房黑哂停左電,佢突然大叫仲攬住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,原來師姐怕黑,佢真係好pure好true,唔似隻air pod雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.我心諗做乜鳩呀?仲執房不如執番劑仲好la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但係我假假地都係正人君子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係含大bsex師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,於是就好gentleman咁送左佢出房,自此佢對我有好感,後尾仲一齊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n  <br />\n  可惜好景不常,師姐突然粒聲唔出走咗,喺佢frd打聽到原來佢啱啱出機場去 havard留學,幻想到食緊hafuck boy d洋腸,我哭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我仲未履行同佢相約在富士山下嘅承諾,就扔底我一個孤零零一個去hafuck<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,我沖岀少林寺跑去機場,攔路嘅雨就好似雪花一樣,凍撚到我郁唔到,呢刻我先知道我又變咗做loser,兩段愛情令我明白到痴情嘅男人只係被嫌棄嘅假鳩,埋單師,要珍惜有得屌閪嘅愛情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 <br />\n   <br />\n  而家諗番其實男人都唔錯,方丈份人好小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,夢(史)遺大師等我番少林寺。 作為ust science仔,我都係同18銅人做下research屌下屎眼算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855048d1212d4de61b631542fae44f81d0b2039a","tid":2286970,"uid":375055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa2d9960acae67d1a56c2a6884ed3c81848dbdaa","tid":2286970,"uid":375055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mHBrGR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mHBrGR.jpg&h=fee61bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等到了失去的時候才後悔莫及<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,相信連登巴絲都有過咁嘅經歷。<br />\n  <br />\n有睇過我之前個post就知道我入左ust之後我前女友為咗個airpod pro比mk仔中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,而我由約佢出嚟到比佢狠狠拒絕嗰刻對條臭雞已經釋懷。決定唔要辜負ust science仔呢個身份,去溝bba女神。<br />\n   <br />\n我收番ust啲毒女令我jer都扯唔起呢句說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,喺我摺拉巴嗰陣,遇到一個超靚嘅bba師姐,可能我有啲靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,佢竟然主動過尼同我講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji